{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-242-odd-triplets","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 242: Male nepravilne serije","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako je skup {1,2,..., $n$}, definišemo $f(n, k)$ kao broj njegovih podskupova sa $k$ elemenata čiji je zbir elemenata neparan. Na primer, $f(5,3) = 4$, zato što skup {1,2,3,4,5} ima četiri podskupa sa 3 elementa čiji je zbir neparan: {1,2,4}, {1,3,5}, {2,3,4} i {2,4,5}.</p>\n<p>Kada sve tri vrednosti $n$, $k$ i $f(n, k)$ su nepravilne, kažemo da formiraju nepravilan podskup $[n, k, f(n, k)]$.</p>\n<p>Postoji samo pet neobičnih malih skupova sa $n \\leq 10$, tj.: $[1, 1, f(1, 1) = 1]$, $[5, 1, f(5, 1) = 3]$, $[5, 5, f(5, 5) = 1]$, $[9, 1, f(9, 1) = 5]$ i $[9, 9, f(9, 9) = 1]$.</p>\n<p>Ni seti ngapi ndogo zisizo za kawaida zipo zenye $n ≤ {10}^{12}$?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f45f1000cf542c50ff71","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301889,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-242-odd-triplets"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function oddTriplets() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\noddTriplets();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>oddTriplets()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>997104142249036700</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(oddTriplets(), 997104142249036700);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-242-odd-triplets",